<plot>In the months after September 11th, media coverage of events in the world affect John. After hearing tragedy after tragedy on the TV and radio John holes himself in his home. His daughter Celeste tries to reach out to him as his only connection to the outside world. As he spirals more and more into paranoia a surprise visit by his daughter and a newly purchased gun almost lead to disaster.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?377772</url></doc>
